00:00:00.790 --> 00:00:04.680
&gt;&gt; From the Library of
Congress in Washington DC.

00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:22.440
All right, everybody comfy?

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:24.170
Everybody happy?

00:00:24.170 --> 00:00:27.470
Everybody ready for an
international Women's Day treat?

00:00:27.470 --> 00:00:32.520
