00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:34.430
that I have with all of you.

00:00:34.430 --> 00:00:40.100
I could not be more honored and
delighted to have the opportunity

00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:45.880
to speak in the Library of Congress
about my area of specialization

00:00:45.880 --> 00:00:49.020
on Women's Day, in Women's History
month at a moment when women

00:00:49.020 --> 00:00:51.950
in Congress are on
strike and marching out.

00:00:51.950 --> 00:00:58.640
It's just a great day to
