00:19:44.680 --> 00:19:52.370
Everything else is
more or less original

00:19:52.370 --> 00:20:00.700
and of course people
also send me stuff

00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:07.320
because they know I'm interested.

00:20:07.320 --> 00:20:16.710
Okay, this is great.

00:20:16.710 --> 00:20:27.010
The era of the twenties series,
we have women really speaking out.

00:20:27.010 --> 00:20:33.570
They are talking about being in
love with women, they are dealing

00:20:33.570 --> 00:20:45.820
with abuse from men,
they are fighting back,

00:20:45.820 --> 00:20:52.510
how do you earn a living, how
do you live outside the lie,

00:20:52.510 --> 00:20:54.700
how do you deal with segregation?

00:20:54.700 --> 00:20:58.900
We are all familiar with the song
Strange Fruit about lynching.

00:20:58.900 --> 00:21:02.920 position:56%
But despite the inevitability of
separating women under Jim Crow Law,

00:21:02.920 --> 00:21:04.650
