00:21:17.570 --> 00:21:21.200
and they are drafted
and women substitute.

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:23.680
And one of the greatest
stories, of course,

00:21:23.680 --> 00:21:32.130
is the International Sweethearts of
Rhythm which was a mixed race band,

00:21:32.130 --> 00:21:40.980 position:56%
very daring, very difficult for them
to find places to stay on the road.

00:21:40.980 --> 00:21:45.950
They included a very famous
trumpet player, Tiny Davis,

00:21:45.950 --> 00:21:51.160
