00:25:22.130 --> 00:25:28.330
who had lost men to
war, draft resistance.

00:25:28.330 --> 00:25:33.030
Eventually Judy Collins, much
later on, recorded a song

00:25:33.030 --> 00:25:34.390
about having an abortion.

00:25:34.390 --> 00:25:39.110
That was not something I
