phenomena was an alternative

00:30:59.720 --> 00:31:01.070
to the bars.

00:31:01.070 --> 00:31:07.630
So it was before Facebook, a space
for the underage and the sober.

00:31:07.630 --> 00:31:11.040
The music on stage openly
named everything that radio

00:31:11.040 --> 00:31:15.650
and news would not talk about
whether it be domestic violence

00:31:15.650 --> 00:31:20.740
or incest, or the lack
of fair wages for women,

00:31:20.740 --> 00:31:25.620
things we're still dealing
with now, being an athlete,

00:31:25.620 --> 00:31:32.670
being a mom who comes after her
kids, being somebody who is poor,

00:31:32.670 --> 00:31:37.580
learning to understand
a person who's ethnicity

00:31:37.580 --> 00:31:39.890 position:56%
and race is different from your own,

00:31:39.890 --> 00:31:42.610
